CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper June 23, 1945, pg. 28, reads: "Merrymakers - The Aniketos Club attended the party given by the Junior Tuberculosis League recently. The merrymakers are seen, left to right, first row: Edward Allen, William Battles, William Monable [Marable], Harold Penn, Mozelle Thompson, James Royal, Raymond Birtha and Robert Fitzpatrick. Second row, left to right: Alvin Daley, Walter Simms, John Cannon, Richard Britton, James Birtha, Clifford [ill. ...art], Howard Groves, Thompson. Third row: Neil Humphries, Bill Nunn and Frank Enty. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Members of Aniketos Club first row from left: Edward Allen, William Battles, William Marable, Harold Penn, Mozelle Thompson, James Royal, Raymond Birtha, Robert Fitzpatrick, standing: Alvin Daley, Walter Simms, Neil Humphries, John Cannon, Bill Nunn, Richard Britton, James Birtha, Clifford [...art], Howard Groves, Frank Enty, Howard Wright, and Mr. Thompson at party given by Junior Tuberculosis League, Loendi Club
